sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant WebApp as Web App<br/>(React)
    participant Gateway as API Gateway<br/>(Kong)
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant DB as Database<br/>(MySQL)

    User->>WebApp: 1. Enter credentials
    WebApp->>Gateway: 2. POST /login
    Gateway->>Auth: 3. Authenticate(email, password)
    Auth->>DB: 4. SELECT * FROM users WHERE email=?
    DB-->>Auth: 5. User record
    Auth-->>Gateway: 6. JWT Token
    Gateway-->>WebApp: 7. 200 OK + Token
    WebApp-->>User: 8. Login success
